        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">On-Site Examination</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Our licensed inspector goes over your entire roof system, from surface to attic, documenting every detail with photographs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Walk-Through of Findings</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">We explain everything in plain language - what is healthy, what needs attention, and what to watch over time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Written Report Delivered</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">A detailed report with photos for your records, useful for insurance, home sales, or planning future maintenance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICE AREA -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
