      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Absolutely. It is free with no strings attached. You are not obligated to purchase anything. We believe honest inspections build trust, and that is how we earn Clearwater homeowners' business when they do need roofing work.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
